data.title: Murder of Elisa Izquierdo, Queens County Podcast
data.meta_description: Life unfolds in complex and sometimes tragic plots, like that of Elisa Izquierdo, a child of Puerto Rican-Cuban origin who touched the hearts of New York and the entire world. Born in 1989 in Brooklyn, her story intertwines with the generosity of a member of the Greek royal family, Prince Michael...
